tosdr.case: You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and for the activities on your account

title: You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and for the activities on your account
quoteText:
If you create an account on the Website, you are responsible for maintaining the
security of your account and its content, and you are fully responsible for all activities
that occur under the account and any other actions taken in connection with the
account.
